1
00:00:00,920 --> 00:00:02,920
Back then.

2
00:00:05,280 --> 00:00:07,600
If only I had made it home on time.

3
00:00:10,640 --> 00:00:13,040
If only I had kept a closer eye on Hazuki.

4
00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:19,360
I wish it had been me who died instead.

5
00:00:21,920 --> 00:00:27,120
I've thought that over and over again.

6
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,160
Why are you crying?

7
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:44,160
Whatever hurts you,

8
00:00:47,080 --> 00:00:48,560
hurts me too.

9
00:00:50,720 --> 00:00:52,120
Mizuki.

10
00:00:54,800 --> 00:00:57,160
Do you think I look like Hazuki?

11
00:01:00,080 --> 00:01:03,520
Your smiles...

12
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:05,000
are very similar.

13
00:01:13,050 --> 00:01:14,150
But I am not her.

14
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:18,680
I am not Hazuki.

15
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:22,200
I am me.

16
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:27,280
I am Mizuki's...

17
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:29,880
non-biological younger brother,

18
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:33,440
and your classmate, Iijima Hinata.

19
00:01:35,700 --> 00:01:36,840
Yeah...

20
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:39,840
If...

21
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:43,800
if Hazuki could see

22
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:48,880
you right now,

23
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,760
wouldn't it break her heart?

24
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:54,660
Huh?

25
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:58,820
Right now... if...

26
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,720
if she is watching over you,

27
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:05,640
she would surely be crying her eyes out.

28
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:25,920
Hinata...

29
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:29,920
Hazuki...

30
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:37,040
Tell me about her.

31
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:37,680
Tell me about Hazuki.

32
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:58,200
I must go, the time has come!

33
00:02:58,880 --> 00:03:00,400
At least tell me your name!

34
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:03,440
Where could the owner

35
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,520
of this glass slipper be?

36
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:07,800
Leave it to me!

37
00:03:10,040 --> 00:03:12,280
I will find her for you, my Prince.

38
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:18,000
Guards! Search every maiden in the kingdom!

39
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:20,840
Find the one whose foot fits this slipper!

40
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:24,800
And so, the royal attendants set out

41
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,640
in search of Cinderella.

42
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,320
Mizuki...

43
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:33,880
it's great to see her so committed to the role.

44
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:36,840
She said she was feeling under the weather, but she seems fine now.

45
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:39,240
Did she eat something strange?

46
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,280
Huh?

47
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,000
It's your turn!

48
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:49,080
Oh no!

49
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:50,480
My stomach hurts so much!

50
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:55,120
Did I eat something bad?

51
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,600
This is a disaster.

52
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:58,880
Cinderella is...

53
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:01,920
Come now! Next maiden,

54
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:04,280
try on the glass slipper.

55
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:09,880
And then, Cinderella appeared in rags.

56
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,920
Cinderella...

57
00:04:21,840 --> 00:04:23,720
Is something wrong?

58
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:36,640
My Prince!

59
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:45,640
I have kept my true feelings hidden all this time.
